title: Baby Play Days for Children Birth to 2 Years of Age
desc: Come and join us for our monthly baby play days. Enjoy access to KYRC toys and play equipment, while getting to know other families with children birth to 2 years of age. Contact the KYRC at 213.252.5600 or  kyrc@lanterman.org  for more information. Program made possible by a contribution from the Fred and June MacMurray Foundation.
